description:
This is a what-if story about, "what if Sonic and Bartleby never met until adulthood!" I shed many tears while making this video... Please enjoy...! :')

(Note that many scenes in this video are very old as this was a video i was making a whole year back, and only finished it now. So please dont go complaining about the quality and all that stuff.)

replies.text:
It's meant to show, that while Sonic is happy, there is still something missing in his heart, and that something is Bartleby. His lover.

It's also thanks to Bartleby, that Sonic realized that out of everyone in the world. Bartleby is the one who cares about him the most. Like when Bartleby buys the gang tickets, you can see the purity in Bartleby's face. 2:03 He almost looks like an angel. lol I wouldn't be surprised if Sonic thought Bartleby was his guardian angel or something at the moment. :) 

And then after that, when everyone makes fun of Bartleby, 2:08 you can actually see the sadness/fear in Sonic's face almost as if he is thinking "Don't! Stop. Leave my lover alone... or I will kill you..." I tink it's a cute lover story really. ;)
